title: Schedule A Tour To See Our Newly Renovated Apartment Homes/Amenities!
posting_body: ['The Durham features just the right blend of charm and the ideal location for your next home.', 'Our community offers a variety of spacious apartment homes ranging from one-bedroom to three-bedroom floor plans.', 'Residents enjoy breathtaking views from our balconies, generous closet space, quartz counters, plank flooring and much, much more!', 'The Durham is nestled in the suburb of Edina with easy access to several major highways.', '-The Playroom with Toys and Child-Friendly Computers', '-Quality-crafted cabinetry with under cabinet lighting', '-Designer tile backsplash with elegant quartz countertops', '-Stay Connected!', 'Wi-Fi in all Amenity Spaces', '-Studio+ Highlighting Wellbeats!', 'Offering a Variety of On-Demand Exercise Programs', '-Dedicated Laundry Facilities with High Efficiency Equipment and Onsite Dry Cleaning', '-Whirlpool stainless steel appliance suite with French door refrigerator and backless range', '-Over 20,000 Sq Ft of Amenities!', '-24-Hour Fitness Center Furnished with Life Fitness Equipment', '-Resident Portal: Enter Maintenance Requests Online when Convenient', '-Professional, Friendly Office and Maintenance Staff', '-The Patio Offerings a Peaceful Outdoor Lounging Space, Accented with Four Gas Grills and a Gas Fire Pit', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'For more information, visit us at: <URL>']
